Accept: application/json
###
GET {{$dotenv s4hanahost}}/sap/opu/odata4/sap/api_prod_hier_prods_srv/srvd_a2x/sap/prodhierprods/0001/ProdUnivHierProdByHierNode/$count
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv s4hana_username}}:{{$dotenv s4hana_password}}
